    "en": {
      "name": "Mind Scan (card)",
      "effect": "While you have a \"Toon\" card in your field or GY, your opponent must keep their hand revealed, also you can look at their Set cards at any time. If you have a Toon monster and a \"Toon\" Spell in your field and/or GY: You can declare 1 card name that is not among the cards/effects activated in this Chain; negate the activated effects of cards with that original name until the end of this turn, while this card is face-up on the field. You can only use this effect of \"Mind Scan\" once per turn.",
      "official": false
    },
